  ylim(0,100) + ggtitle("RC-ls Tower: Relative Humidity")+
  theme(axis.title.y = element_text(margin = margin(t = 0, r = 17, b = 0, l = 0)))

rcls.plot2 <- ggplot(rcls[12125:nrow(rcls),], aes(y=RH, x=TIMESTAMP_START)) + geom_point(alpha=0.01, color='red', size=3) +
  ylim(-9900,-10100) + ggtitle("Missing data")
